title: You're the GM Returns! (Trade Deadline Edition)
itunes:title: You're the GM Returns! (Trade Deadline Edition)
description:
Often imitated, never duplicated... back by popular demand... it's the long-awaited return of You're the GM! Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe take turns assuming the identity of an NFL General Manager (or head coach) making a call to another team seeking a big-time, franchise-changing trade ahead of next week's November 1st deadline. This is one episode you don't want to miss.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
